PROTOTYPE
---------

1. Option to input audio - currently an audio file works and sockets too :)
2. Parse audio to text - working for english -> working with sockets :)
3. Input text to model - TBD
4. Get response - TBD
5. Output response as speech - currently working with ElevenLabs -> need to integrate OR Azure is better option in terms of free minutes and quality

DESIGN
------


User inputs audio -> audio transcribed (STT) -> Transcribe output to LLMmodel -> LLM outputs text -> TTS using Eleven Labs -> Output to end user